            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi <lb n="2"/>pro salute Impe<lb break="no" n="3"/>ratorum Severi <lb n="4"/>et Antonini <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> conser<lb break="no" n="5"/>vatori Augustorum <lb n="6"/>dominorum nos<lb break="no" n="7"/>trorum <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Gallu<lb break="no" n="8"/>s <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> legatus eorum <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> cum suis <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur durch eine Abschrift bekannt. Z. 7/8: überliefert ist C(aius) I(ulius) Gallu/s</p>
            </div>
